        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1718607045" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1627431253005293102">I stumbled over Gene Wolfe and the Book of the New Sun via Neil Gaiman, who was praising it highly.<br/><br/>I can definitely see why. The prose is beautiful. Gene Wolfe has a wonderful way with words. It&apos;s almost like reading poetry.<br/><br/>Not much happens in this first of four books, but it was an easy read, immersive and beautiful. I connected with the narrator almost immediately and can&apos;t wait to find out what happens to Severian the Torturer.</span>
  <span id="freeText1627431253005293102" style="display:none">I stumbled over Gene Wolfe and the Book of the New Sun via Neil Gaiman, who was praising it highly.<br /><br />I can definitely see why. The prose is beautiful. Gene Wolfe has a wonderful way with words. It's almost like reading poetry.<br /><br />Not much happens in this first of four books, but it was an easy read, immersive and beautiful. I connected with the narrator almost immediately and can't wait to find out what happens to Severian the Torturer.</span>
